satellite = SatelliteStabilization(u1=lambda t, s: 0.0, u2=lambda t, s: 0.2 *
    s[0] * s[2], u3=lambda t, s: -s[0] * s[1])
p0, q0, r0 = 24, 16, 16
sol = scipy.integrate.solve_ivp(fun=satellite.model_eq_np, t_span=[0, 1],
    y0=[p0, q0, r0, 0], method='RK45', t_eval=np.linspace(0, 1, num=101))
assert np.all(sol.y[0] == p0)
